{
  "texts": [
    "Our iterative DPO baselines are implemented using the trl library with PyTorch FSDP2 enabled to support efficient distributed training at all model scales.",
    "For evaluation, we similarly select the checkpoint that maximizes the validation reward.",
    "We repeat this process for 3 rounds.",
    "RL-based methods (RL-Logit, RLVR, and RARO).",
    "All RL-based methods-RL-Logit, RLVR, and RARO-are implemented on top of the verl framework (Sheng et al., 2024), a flexible and efficient RL framework for LLM post-training."
  ]
}